name: ELI GOES TO THE STORE
description:
Eli's mom wants him to buy vegetables and vegan tacos. But Eli is cool and he's not a nerd. so he's gonna get OTHER things...

LOW EFFORT GAME

ASSETS ARE MINE EXCEPT FOR THE BACKGROUND AND THE MUSIC PLAYED IN THE CREDITS ("Door" by Xean)

use the arrow keys to move and double jump.
